### Authorization from Scratch in NodeJs

Coming from a rails background, the first thing I learned was authorization, following the Ruby on Rails Tutorial by Michael Hartl. It was long after that I discovered how much easy it was to use something like Device to manage my apps authorization procedure. However, after teaching rails I realized how important was the understanding of authorization for an app developer. A simple sign up/in/out procedure can be defined in the following way

